# ERP Test Gate

功能完成不代表可以上線。

## 最小必跑（依需求增減）

## Minimum Test Matrix

### Happy Path
- normal create
- normal post
- normal void

### Boundary
- zero
- minimum
- maximum
- exact remaining qty
- one unit over
- date boundary

### Multi-line
- same product multiple lines
- same SO item multiple Lots
- multiple SO items same Lot where allowed
- different prices

### Retry
- double click
- same request retry
- timeout retry
- same key different payload

### Concurrency
- two users same Lot
- two users same SO
- two users same AR
- POST vs VOID
- payment vs VOID

### Failure Injection
- fail after first mutation
- fail before AR
- fail after AR
- fail before ledger
- fail after ledger

Expected: full rollback

### Permission
- no session
- wrong role
- no action permission
- forged actor

### Parity（OLD vs NEW）
- amount
- qty
- status
- pricing
- promotion
- credit
- cumulative

### Migration
- old data
- duplicate data
- null data
- rollback

## Gate Result

測試輸出：

- PASS
- FAIL
- BLOCKER
- NOT TESTED

任何核心案例 NOT TESTED：不得 GO FOR PRODUCTION。

## 輸出
- 測試清單 + 結果（PASS/FAIL）
- 發現差異：列出差異與處理決策（保留為技術債或修正）

